#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.barh.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.barh"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:1
#: of
msgid "Make a horizontal bar plot."
msgstr "制作一个水平条形图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:3
#: of
msgid ""
"A horizontal bar plot is a plot that presents quantitative data with "
"rectangular bars with lengths proportional to the values that they "
"represent. A bar plot shows comparisons among discrete categories. One "
"axis of the plot shows the specific categories being compared, and the "
"other axis represents a measured value."
msgstr ""
"水平条形图是用矩形条表示定量数据的图形，其长度与所代表的数值成比例。"
"条形图显示了离散类别之间的比较。图形的一个轴显示正在比较的特定类别，另"
"一个轴表示测量值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:9
#: of
msgid ""
"Allows plotting of one column versus another. If not specified, the index"
" of the DataFrame is used."
msgstr "允许绘制一列相对于另一列的图。如果未指定，则使用 DataFrame 的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:12
#: of
msgid ""
"Allows plotting of one column versus another. If not specified, all "
"numerical columns are used."
msgstr "允许绘制一列相对于另一列的图。如果未指定，则使用所有数值列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:15
#: of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The color for each of the DataFrame's columns. Possible values are:  - A "
"single color string referred to by name, RGB or RGBA code,     for "
"instance 'red' or '#a98d19'.  - A sequence of color strings referred to "
"by name, RGB or RGBA     code, which will be used for each column "
"recursively. For     instance ['green','yellow'] each column's bar will "
"be filled in     green or yellow, alternatively. If there is only a "
"single column to     be plotted, then only the first color from the color"
" list will be     used.  - A dict of the form {column name : color}, so "
"that each column will be     colored accordingly. For example, if your "
"columns are called `a` and     `b`, then passing {'a': 'green', 'b': "
"'red'} will color bars for     column `a` in green and bars for column "
"`b` in red."
msgstr ""
"DataFrame 每一列的颜色。可能的值包括：  - 通过名称、RGB 或 RGBA 代码引用"
"的单个颜色字符串，例如 'red' 或 '#a98d19'。  - 通过名称、RGB 或 RGBA 代码"
"引用的颜色字符串序列，将递归地用于每一列。例如 ['green','yellow']，每列的"
"条形将交替填充为绿色或黄色。如果只绘制一列，则只会使用颜色列表中的第一个"
"颜色。  - 形如 {列名 : 颜色} 的字典，以便每列都按相应颜色着色。例如，如果"
"您的列名为 `a` 和 `b`，那么传递 {'a': 'green', 'b': 'red'} 将使列 `a` 的"
"条形为绿色，列 `b` 的条形为红色。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:15
#: of
msgid "The color for each of the DataFrame's columns. Possible values are:"
msgstr "DataFrame各列的颜色。可能的值包括："

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:17
#: of
msgid "A single color string referred to by name, RGB or RGBA code,"
msgstr "通过名称、RGB或RGBA代码引用的单个颜色字符串，"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:18
#: of
msgid "for instance 'red' or '#a98d19'."
msgstr "例如 'red' 或 '#a98d19'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:20
#: of
msgid "A sequence of color strings referred to by name, RGB or RGBA"
msgstr "通过名称、RGB或RGBA代码引用的颜色字符串序列"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:21
#: of
msgid ""
"code, which will be used for each column recursively. For instance "
"['green','yellow'] each column's bar will be filled in green or yellow, "
"alternatively. If there is only a single column to be plotted, then only "
"the first color from the color list will be used."
msgstr ""
"代码，将递归地用于每一列。例如 ['green','yellow']，每个列的条形将交替填充"
"绿色或黄色。如果只有一列要绘制，则只使用颜色列表中的第一个颜色。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:27
#: of
msgid "A dict of the form {column name"
msgstr "一个 {列名"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:-1
#: of
msgid "color}, so that each column will be"
msgstr "颜色} 形式的字典，这样每一列都将"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:28
#: of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"colored accordingly. For example, if your columns are called `a` and `b`,"
" then passing {'a': 'green', 'b': 'red'} will color bars for column `a` "
"in green and bars for column `b` in red."
msgstr ""
"被相应地着色。例如，如果您的列名为 `a` 和 `b`，那么传递 {'a': 'green', 'b"
"': 'red'} 将使列 `a` 的条形为绿色，列 `b` 的条形为红色。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:32
#: of
msgid "Additional keyword arguments are documented in :meth:`DataFrame.plot`."
msgstr "其他关键字参数在 :meth:`DataFrame.plot` 中有文档说明。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:35
#: of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"An ndarray is returned with one :class:`matplotlib.axes.Axes` per column "
"when ``subplots=True``.      See Also     --------     "
"DataFrame.plot.bar: Vertical bar plot.     DataFrame.plot : Make plots of"
" DataFrame using matplotlib.     matplotlib.axes.Axes.bar : Plot a "
"vertical bar plot using matplotlib.      Examples     --------     Basic "
"example      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> import "
"maxframe.tensor as mt         >>> import maxframe.dataframe as md"
"         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'lab': ['A', 'B', 'C'], 'val': [10, 30, "
"20]})         >>> ax = df.plot.barh(x='lab', y='val')      Plot a whole "
"DataFrame to a horizontal bar plot      .. plot::         :context: "
"close-figs          >>> speed = [0.1, 17.5, 40, 48, 52, 69, 88]         "
">>> lifespan = [2, 8, 70, 1.5, 25, 12, 28]         >>> index = ['snail', "
"'pig', 'elephant',         ...          'rabbit', 'giraffe', 'coyote', "
"'horse']         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'speed': speed,         ..."
"                    'lifespan': lifespan}, index=index)         >>> ax = "
"df.plot.barh()      Plot stacked barh charts for the DataFrame      .. "
"plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> ax = "
"df.plot.barh(stacked=True)      We can specify colors for each column"
"      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> ax = "
"df.plot.barh(color={\"speed\": \"red\", \"lifespan\": \"green\"})      "
"Plot a column of the DataFrame to a horizontal bar plot      .. plot::"
"         :context: close-figs          >>> speed = [0.1, 17.5, 40, 48, "
"52, 69, 88]         >>> lifespan = [2, 8, 70, 1.5, 25, 12, 28]         "
">>> index = ['snail', 'pig', 'elephant',         ...          'rabbit', "
"'giraffe', 'coyote', 'horse']         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'speed': "
"speed,         ...                    'lifespan': lifespan}, index=index)"
"         >>> ax = df.plot.barh(y='speed')      Plot DataFrame versus the "
"desired column      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> "
"speed = [0.1, 17.5, 40, 48, 52, 69, 88]         >>> lifespan = [2, 8, 70,"
" 1.5, 25, 12, 28]         >>> index = ['snail', 'pig', 'elephant',"
"         ...          'rabbit', 'giraffe', 'coyote', 'horse']         >>>"
" df = md.DataFrame({'speed': speed,         ...                    "
"'lifespan': lifespan}, index=index)         >>> ax = "
"df.plot.barh(x='lifespan')"
msgstr ""
"当 ``subplots=True`` 时，返回一个包含每个列对应一个 :class:`matplotlib."
"axes.Axes` 的 ndarray。      参见     --------     DataFrame.plot.bar: "
"垂直条形图。     DataFrame.plot : 使用 matplotlib 绘制 DataFrame 的图表。"
"     matplotlib.axes.Axes.bar : 使用 matplotlib 绘制垂直条形图。      "
"示例     --------     基础示例      .. plot::         :context: close-"
"figs          >>> import maxframe.tensor as mt         >>> import "
"maxframe.dataframe as md         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'lab': ['A', 'B',"
" 'C'], 'val': [10, 30, 20]})         >>> ax = df.plot.barh(x='lab', y='"
"val')      将整个 DataFrame 绘制为水平条形图      .. plot::         :"
"context: close-figs          >>> speed = [0.1, 17.5, 40, 48, 52, 69, 88] "
"        >>> lifespan = [2, 8, 70, 1.5, 25, 12, 28]         >>> index = ['"
"snail', 'pig', 'elephant',         ...          'rabbit', 'giraffe', '"
"coyote', 'horse']         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'speed': speed,         "
"...                    'lifespan': lifespan}, index=index)         >>> ax"
" = df.plot.barh()      为 DataFrame 绘制堆叠的水平条形图      .. plot::  "
"       :context: close-figs          >>> ax = df.plot.barh(stacked=True) "
"     我们可以为每列指定颜色      .. plot::         :context: close-figs  "
"        >>> ax = df.plot.barh(color={\"speed\": \"red\", \"lifespan\": \""
"green\"})      将 DataFrame 的一列绘制为水平条形图      .. plot::        "
" :context: close-figs          >>> speed = [0.1, 17.5, 40, 48, 52, 69, 88"
"]         >>> lifespan = [2, 8, 70, 1.5, 25, 12, 28]         >>> index = "
"['snail', 'pig', 'elephant',         ...          'rabbit', 'giraffe', '"
"coyote', 'horse']         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'speed': speed,         "
"...                    'lifespan': lifespan}, index=index)         >>> ax"
" = df.plot.barh(y='speed')      按指定列绘制 DataFrame      .. plot::    "
"     :context: close-figs          >>> speed = [0.1, 17.5, 40, 48, 52, 69"
", 88]         >>> lifespan = [2, 8, 70, 1.5, 25, 12, 28]         >>> "
"index = ['snail', 'pig', 'elephant',         ...          'rabbit', '"
"giraffe', 'coyote', 'horse']         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'speed': "
"speed,         ...                    'lifespan': lifespan}, index=index)"
"         >>> ax = df.plot.barh(x='lifespan')"

